<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">• قال الدَّارَقُطْنِيّ:</span> ضعيف. <span class="c2">«السنن»</span> ٢ ٩٦.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">• وقال الدَّارَقُطْنِيّ:</span> ذاهب الحديث. <span class="c2">«تهذيب التهذيب»</span> ٤ ٥٢.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>